  "text": "Should scoped style be appliad to teleported elements ?\n\n### Version\r\n3.0.0-rc.10\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://codesandbox.io/s/elegant-neumann-6j0rl](https://codesandbox.io/s/elegant-neumann-6j0rl)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nTeleport an element with scoped styles\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nIMO opinion we should be able to somehow apply scoped styles to teleported elements\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nscoped styles are not applied\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
